09:56.300 --> 09:56.940
Prendi la medicina

10:20.259 --> 10:20.779
Ruan Yu

10:23.739 --> 10:24.180
Dai

10:24.899 --> 10:25.700
Prima prendi la medicina

10:30.580 --> 10:31.060
Dai

10:40.420 --> 10:41.820
